{"tid":1932184,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓市疫境】賢文禮士四房撻訂戶重售　相隔8日賣平6%","createTime":"2020-03-18T14:43:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T00:49:08.000Z","uid":101341,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"42f51c54bf52f037eb9de098e7cbe597fcb5d0e9","tid":1932184,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T14:43:23.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情爆發，打撃全球經濟信心，華懋集團旗下九龍塘新盤賢文禮士錄得一宗撻訂重售個案。項目第3座9樓A室的四房戶，實用面積1,514方呎，原於本月8日以約3,628萬元出售，惟買家簽訂臨時買賣合約後，交易再未有進展，料遭沒收5%訂金約181.4萬元。<br />\n<br />\n發展商其後將單位重售，昨日透過招標以3,401.8萬元沽出，呎價約2.24萬元，該成交價較3月8日的價格低約226.2萬元，換言之，同一單位相隔8日約賣平6%。"},{"pid":"b4c824687fbe5e219af7e7d3c0fbe72d232a93de","tid":1932184,"uid":19725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:37:50.000Z","msg":"追佢兩球差價"},{"pid":"2670b9fc59e6580dd4166b4bb96227314af9ece9","tid":1932184,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4c824687fbe5e219af7e7d3c0fbe72d232a93de","tid":1932184,"uid":19725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:37:50.000Z","msg":"追佢兩球差價"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:54:07.000Z","msg":"新例實施後臨約追到？"},{"pid":"c91efd59b552f0fbacd40f2f58e1e931736a1603","tid":1932184,"uid":240276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4c824687fbe5e219af7e7d3c0fbe72d232a93de","tid":1932184,"uid":19725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:37:50.000Z","msg":"追佢兩球差價"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T22:33:47.000Z","msg":"應該簽正式合約先會追"},{"pid":"ce63a951557d5ca7f69d15948997eb2cccf28447","tid":1932184,"uid":48584,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T22:36:56.000Z","msg":"訂金邊個袋？"},{"pid":"d8d800973aab9de7f2fa7652bef7d55f8c1033a9","tid":1932184,"uid":202351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce63a951557d5ca7f69d15948997eb2cccf28447","tid":1932184,"uid":48584,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T22:36:56.000Z","msg":"訂金邊個袋？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-1